title: Are there like no other Iron/Bronze players???
body: All I wanted was to play some Ranked for the Annie-Versary skin :/

replies.body:
You don't need to play ranked for the skin. I got it in normals. I think even URF may work for it.

P.S: Everyone is playing URF.

I know I don't *have* to played Ranked, but I want to because I get a skin AND I potentially climb.

Queue just passed the 4 hour mark though... I'm starting to believe this is life telling me not to play League anymore XD
